contentrichtext.text: {{other_people5|Yoshi (disambiguation)}} '''Yoshii''' ({{lang-ja|吉井}}) is the name of several places in Japan: *[[Yoshii, Fukuoka]], a former town in Fukuoka Prefecture *[[Yoshii, Gunma]], a former town in Gunma Prefecture *[[Yoshii, Nagasaki]], a former town in Nagasaki Prefecture *[[Yoshii, Okayama (Akaiwa)]] （吉井町）, a former town in Akaiwa District, Okayama Prefecture *[[Yoshii, Okayama (Shitsuki)]] （芳井町）, a former town in Shitsuki District, Okayama Prefecture Yoshii can also be a Japanese surname: * [[Yoshii Isamu]], poet * [[Masato Yoshii]], baseball player [[The Jim Yoshii Pile-Up]] is a band in Oakland, California. {{disambig}} [[Category:Place name disambiguation pages]] [[Category:Surnames]]
